headline: Fifth Third Bancorp Announces Cash Dividends
summary: CINCINNATI, December 08, 2025--Today, Fifth Third Bancorp announced the declaration of cash dividends on its common shares, Series H preferred shares, Series I preferred shares, Series J preferred shares, Series K preferred shares, and Class B Series A preferred shares.
